Photography – Luxury Portfolio Website

A modern dark-themed photography portfolio website designed using HTML and CSS.

📌 Features

Dark luxury UI design

Gold accent styling

Fixed glass-effect header

Fullscreen hero section

Portfolio grid layout

Service cards with hover effects

Styled contact form

Responsive design

🛠 Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3

Flexbox

CSS Grid

Google Fonts

🚀 How to Run

Download or clone the repository.

Open index.html in any web browser.

Ensure photography.css is in the same folder.

🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:

Dark theme portfolio design

Layout structuring using Flexbox & Grid

Responsive web design

UI spacing and typography balance

Hover effects and transitions

📄 License

For educational and personal portfolio use.
